about.title: Planning
about.description: Strategic Blueprinting: I meticulously plan applications from inception, leveraging tools like wireframes and Entity-Relationship Diagrams (ERDs). This ensures a solid foundation for development.

about.title: Design
about.description: Visual Craftsmanship: I specialize in creating visually captivating applications, combining aesthetics with user-centric design principles for an engaging and delightful user experience.

about.title: Maintenance
about.description: Continuous Enhancement: Beyond the launch, I ensure your application remains at its best. From bug fixes to feature updates, I handle the ongoing maintenance to keep your application running smoothly.

about.title: Deployment
about.description: Global Visibility: Taking your application from development to the live environment, I handle the deployment process. Your creation will be ready for the world to explore, ensuring a seamless transition to the online space.

projects.name: SpendWise
projects.description: SpendWise is my front end capstone project. It is a web-based budget tracker application where users can log in and manage their income and expenses.

projects.name: TechTasker
projects.description: TechTasker is my full-stack capstone project. It is a web-based work order crud application where supervisors can create, edit, and delete work orders, and assign them to employees. Employees can view and update the status of work orders.
